The paper deals with privacy attacks on network traffic, specifically website fingerprinting attacks. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also uses machine learning techniques to classify traces of cache activity, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the effectiveness of the attack in different environments, which could fall under the categories of systems and control (cs.SY), software engineering (cs.SE), and programming languages (cs.PL).
